INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (323,'025','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 is filled with fluctuating fortunes and unpredictable changes. While there are periods when you can spend time leisurely like a carefree sage under clear wind and bright moonlight, there also exist times of frustration when things don''t go as planned. Though good energy arrives as yin and yang harmonize and all things revive, the fortune shows a pattern of good beginnings but difficult endings, creating instability like living away from home in a foreign land. Just as planting beans yields beans and planting red beans yields red beans, you must clearly understand cause and effect relationships and judge carefully. Remember that there is a high mountain ahead and an even higher ridge behind - even after overcoming one hurdle, another difficulty may await. However, like sweet rain after drought, when the right time comes, warm energy returns, so an attitude of patience while waiting for that time is necessary.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
Wealth fortune shows stark contrast between the first and second halves. In the first half, like a dragon meeting clear seawater, unexpected joyful wealth may arrive. Especially in February, household celebrations bring expected wealth increase through descendants or family. Since wealth lies in the northern direction, consider business or investments related to northern regions. In November, even small wealth will surely come, so heading north can bring profits. However, in the second half, even when gaining wealth it''s difficult to save and expenses are high, so advance preparation is needed. In May and June, expanding business too ambitiously proves disadvantageous, so refrain from excessive expansion or investment and focus on stable financial management. Investments or business toward the south may turn from fortune to misfortune, requiring caution.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
Career fortune also experiences severe ups and downs this year. In January, circumstances are difficult with no work and business challenges, making it hard to achieve results despite fatigue. From March, avoid trying to sustain business or making hasty decisions, acting prudently instead. In June and July, rushing to finish work is dangerous, and though intentions exist, accomplishing them proves difficult, like having a head but no tail with insufficient results. In August, taking eastern and northern matters lightly causes disputes, requiring careful attention when planning or starting work. In September, it''s like trying to fly without wings, making even small-scale operations feel futile. However, from November, discarding old and seeking new brings joyful opportunities ahead worth challenging with full effort. With patience while waiting for the right time, good opportunities will surely arrive.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
In love and marriage matters, special caution is needed in relationships. In March and May, associating with wrong people will surely bring harm, so thoroughly assess partners and choose carefully. In March, even without quarreling, gossip may arise, so avoiding rumors and staying quiet is advisable. In October, wavering without firm conviction makes hasty decisions unwise - take time to judge. In December, joyful and sad events may contrast, so when things don''t go well, waiting rather than forcing progress is wise. In February, household celebrations may bring good news of marriage proposals or family expansion. Overall, rather than rushing hastily, developing relationships carefully while taking time to communicate and understand partners is important.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Special attention to health management is required this year. In January and April, unless related to legal matters, health problems may arise requiring advance prevention. In April, officials may feel unwell or stressed from administrative matters, so getting health checkups and sufficient rest is advisable. In July and August, beware of recklessness, as losses or unexpected accidents may follow, requiring special caution. In September, easily becoming stuck unable to advance or retreat, don''t make futile plans or attempt excessive schedules. In October, hearts filled with worry make staying quietly at home the best choice. Avoid going out or excessive activities, focusing on stress management and mental health. Overall, not overexerting while monitoring your body''s condition, maintaining regular living and sufficient rest to protect health is important.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
In relationships, particularly selective and cautious attitudes are required. In March, associating with wrong people will surely bring harm, so when forming new connections, thoroughly assess the other party''s character before judging. Even without quarreling, gossip may arise, so be careful with words and actions, being cautious not to get involved in unnecessary rumors. In May, unexpected sacrifices may occur, so be especially careful in making friends, and since losses may follow, be prudent when handling all matters. In July and August, worries may arise from document or contract issues, so check and handle with sincere attention. In October, avoid romantic affairs or disputes, as resulting gossip is hard to escape - staying quiet is the best policy. In November, though feeling loneliness like deep mountain valleys leaving nowhere to rely or sit, maintaining your station and exercising restraint can avoid this misfortune. Overall, wisdom is needed to strengthen relationships with trustworthy people while avoiding suspicious connections.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
Academic and self-development fortune requires patience and persistence this year. In January, though feeling tired with no work and slow study progress, don''t give up and work steadily. In June and July, rushing to finish work is dangerous, so when setting academic goals, establishing gradual and achievable plans is important. In September, feeling frustrated like trying to fly without wings, this is merely temporary stagnation - don''t be impatient. From November, discarding old and seeking new brings joyful opportunities ahead. Challenging new study fields or certification acquisition can yield good results. In December, timing must be kept well - don''t rush hastily but maintain your pace with steady dedication. Overall, abandoning haste and calmly walking your path will bring good results eventually, even if delayed.','January is a month when achieving results is difficult despite fatigue, with no work and difficult business circumstances. Though welcoming the new year, insufficient work and continuing economic difficulties are possible. Rather than forcing matters, facing reality and doing your best within possible limits is important.

If no legal problems or government issues exist, household worries or difficulties may arise requiring advance preparation and prevention. Facilitating family communication and making efforts to resolve household problems early is necessary.

If you meet good people, peace will come to your person, so look forward with a positive mind. Good connections can greatly help navigate difficult times.

Wealth fortune is poor, so refrain from large expenditures and consume only minimally necessary things. At work, quietly focus on your tasks, postponing new projects or business being wise. Pay attention to health management, with sufficient rest and nutritional intake needed. The northern direction is relatively stable, with lucky colors being black and gray. Spend time quietly while preparing for next month.','February is a fortunate month when household celebrations will surely bring joy through descendants or family expansion. Good news may arrive or joyful family member increases may occur, so welcome this with a grateful heart.

Since wealth lies in the northern direction, seeking can surely obtain it. Work related to northern regions or dealings with people living in the north are favorable. Actively utilize the north to pursue wealth.

Focus on finishing work. Rather than starting new work, organizing and completing current ongoing matters is important. Clean completion establishes foundation for advancing to the next stage.

Do not proceed toward the south. Southern business or travel may turn fortune to misfortune, so avoidance is advisable. Greed to expand business greatly can also work disadvantageously, so maintain your station. Eastern and northern directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being white and blue. Spend the month sharing joy with family.','March is a month requiring special caution as western and southern directions are harmful. Avoiding western or southern business trips, travel, or business expansion is wise. These directions may work disadvantageously for fortune.

Do not try to sustain business or make hasty decisions. Forcibly trying to expand current work or hastily making important decisions can cause poor results. Think and judge carefully.

Associating with wrong people will surely bring harm, so be especially careful. When forming new connections, thoroughly assess the other party''s character, confirming trustworthiness before developing relationships.

Even without quarreling, gossip may exist, so avoid rumors. Be careful with words and actions, refraining from unnecessary arguments or conversations, with staying quiet being best. Both wealth and career fortune are ordinary, so focus on maintaining status quo. Eastern and northern directions are relatively safe, with lucky colors being green and brown. Spend the month carefully.','April is a month when official duties or power weigh upon you but officials'' persons are uncomfortable. Workplace responsibilities may increase or work burdens intensify, causing stress. Be careful not to overwork, paying special attention to health management.

Or gossip from government or legal problems may abound, so be careful and move cautiously. To avoid getting involved in legal disputes or government office problems, handle all matters transparently and refrain from rash behavior.

If celebrations occur, this misfortune will disappear, but otherwise fear of great heartbreak exists. If good news or joyful events occur, difficulties may resolve, so maintain a positive mind and don''t lose hope.

At work, quietly dedicate yourself to your duties, refraining from unnecessary words or actions while acting prudently. Wealth fortune is ordinary, avoiding large investments or expenditures being advisable. Get health checkups, take sufficient rest, and care for your body. The northern direction is relatively stable, with lucky colors being gray and black. Spend the month carefully.','May is a month when you must not go south. Absolutely avoid southern travel, business trips, or business as fortune may turn to misfortune. This direction works very disadvantageously for fortune.

Greed to expand business too greatly is disadvantageous. Excessive expansion or excessive investment may bring losses instead, so maintain your station and promote work within realistic limits.

If you meet undesirable people, you will face unexpected sacrifices, so be especially careful in making friends. When forming new connections, thoroughly assess partners, confirming trustworthiness before developing relationships.

Since losses or unexpected accidents may follow, be prudent when handling all matters. When making contracts or deals, check thoroughly and don''t make rash decisions. Pay special attention to safety, avoiding dangerous activities.

Both wealth and career fortune are poor, so postpone new challenges and focus on maintaining status quo. Health also requires attention, with stress management and sufficient rest being important. Eastern and northern directions are relatively safe, with lucky colors being white and light blue. Spend the month carefully.','June is a month when you must not go west. Absolutely avoid western travel, business trips, or business as fortune may turn to misfortune. This direction works very disadvantageously for fortune.

Rushing to finish work is dangerous. Hasty rushing may cause mistakes or poor results, so handle work carefully with sufficient time. Abandoning impatience and proceeding calmly is important.

Since work has difficulties, even seeking work is hard to accomplish. Rather than finding new jobs or starting projects, maintaining current situations while pursuing stability is wise.

Though intentions exist, accomplishing according to will is difficult, like having a head but no tail. Plans may be made but implementation difficult or results insufficient, so don''t have excessive expectations and approach realistically.

At work, quietly focus on your tasks, avoiding unnecessary changes or challenges. Wealth fortune is also poor, so minimize expenditures and focus on savings. Pay attention to health management, avoiding overwork and taking sufficient rest. Eastern and northern directions are relatively safe, with lucky colors being green and gray.','July is a month requiring caution against recklessness. Blindly promoting work or making hasty judgments can lead to great difficulties, so handle all matters carefully and act after sufficient thought.

Fear exists that losses or unexpected accidents may follow. Pay special attention to safety, avoiding dangerous activities or excessive schedules. When making contracts or deals, check thoroughly and don''t make rash decisions.

Since worries exist about document or contract leaks or problems, sincere attention is needed. Store important documents safely, check contract contents thoroughly, and handle transparently to avoid legal problems.

Taking eastern and northern matters lightly causes disputes. Even for eastern or northern related matters, don''t be careless but handle carefully. Cautious attitudes are needed in all directions.

If not careful when planning, discussing, or starting work, avoiding disputes becomes difficult. Before starting new projects or business, review sufficiently and decide after consulting with trustworthy people. Both wealth and career fortune require attention, so focus on maintaining status quo. Lucky colors are gray and brown.','August is a frustrating month like trying to fly without wings. Even with desired work, circumstances don''t permit or abilities are insufficient making execution difficult. Rather than forcing promotion, acknowledge reality and do your best within possible limits.

Like the sun and moon unable to gain wings, it''s lamentable. Opportunities to demonstrate abilities may not exist, or feeling frustration when environments don''t support. However, don''t be impatient but endure while waiting for the right time.

Even small-scale operations feel futile, in situations unable to advance or retreat. Falling into dilemmas, postponing important decisions and maintaining current states is wise.

Since fortune is ominous, don''t think of or make futile plans. Unrealistic or excessive plans are likely to fail, requiring realistic and prudent approaches.

At work, quietly focus on your tasks, avoiding new challenges or changes. Wealth fortune is also poor, so refrain from unnecessary expenditures and focus on savings. Pay attention to health management, managing stress appropriately and taking sufficient rest. Lucky colors are white and pale yellow.','September is a month when hearts filled with worry make staying quietly at home better. Rather than going out or doing active work, taking rest at home and finding mental stability is advisable.

Do not go out or promote work. Starting new work or doing external activities may cause problems instead, so stay quietly focusing on maintaining status quo.

Doing romantic affairs or causing disputes makes avoiding resulting gossip difficult. Avoid romantic relationships or unnecessary arguments, being careful with words and actions, with staying quiet being best.

Though wealth can be obtained, it''s difficult to save so be careful in advance. Even with income, many expenditures make saving difficult, so thoroughly manage finances and reduce unnecessary consumption.

At work, quietly dedicate yourself to your tasks, acting prudently in relationships too. Pay special attention to health management, with meditation or light exercise helping mental stability. Staying stably at home is best, with lucky colors being gray and black.','October is a lonely month like deep mountain valleys leaving nowhere to rely or sit. Though feeling isolation or frustration without people to rely on, this is temporary so don''t be too discouraged.

Unless great misfortune, avoiding losses or unexpected accidents is difficult, so be careful of others. Be wary of surrounding people, keeping distance from untrustworthy individuals, and checking thoroughly when making contracts or deals.

Being greedy will fail instead, so maintaining your station and exercising restraint can avoid this misfortune. Don''t be excessively greedy but focus on work possible in your position, and acting humbly and prudently can avoid difficulties.

Both wealth and career fortune are poor, so postpone new challenges and focus on maintaining status quo. Health also requires attention, with stress management and sufficient rest being important.

Act prudently in relationships too, avoiding unnecessary meetings or gatherings being advisable. Spend time quietly at home finding inner stability. Lucky colors are brown and gray. Spend the month carefully while maintaining your station.','November is a month when even small wealth will surely come, so you should properly head north. Northern business trips, travel, or business are favorable, and dealings or cooperation with northern region people will bring wealth.

Discarding old and seeking new brings joyful opportunities waiting ahead. Breaking away from old methods or familiar things to try new things can yield good results. Don''t fear change and accept it actively.

This is a time worth challenging with full effort. Challenging previously hesitated work or new projects with courage has high success possibilities. Approach actively with confidence.

As wealth fortune rises, consider northern investments or business. New opportunities may arrive at work too, so participate actively and demonstrate your abilities.

Health also recovers during this period, so build strength through consistent exercise and regular living. Relationships also improve and new connections may arrive. The northern direction is most auspicious, with lucky colors being blue and black. Challenge actively and seize opportunities.','December is a month when joy and sadness contrast as the mind wavers without firm conviction. With severe emotional ups and downs making decisions difficult, postpone important decisions and judge after sufficient thought.

Since work doesn''t go well, don''t rush to promote work. Rushing may cause mistakes or poor results, so handle carefully with time.

Being wrongly greedy will bring harm instead. Refrain from excessive greed and maintain your station, promoting work within realistic limits being wise.

Since fortune suddenly reversed, it''s neither small nor large. Flowing ordinarily without major changes, focus on maintaining status quo and pursuing stability.

Timing must be kept well. Don''t rush hastily but wait for appropriate timing, with wisdom needed to act when opportunities come.

At work, quietly focus on your tasks, and thoroughly manage wealth too. Pay attention to health management, having time to wrap up the year well and prepare for next year. All directions are relatively ordinary, with lucky colors being white and gold. Wrap up the year carefully.','2025-03-02 03:02:01.089982+00','e');

